entry.title: Blunt Beast
entry.summary:
Vendor: the dabbing specialists
Type:
Price: 12.00

Blunt Beast Smoking Wand

[click to view our shipping policies]

Description for Part Number 6919

Blunt smokers, you might need this gigantic eleven-inch smoking wand! These wooden handled "smoking wands" created in the USA with US, sustainably harvested hardwood lumber are unmatched and unbeatable. We thought you might want these around your crib too.

  • An 11" Smoking Wand
  • Bloodwood
  • Superb Quality Roach Clip
  • Great For Any Rolled Treasure
  • USA Hardwood
  • Each One Is Unique

Description from the Mystic Timber website:

"The Blunt Beast (formerly the Classic Beast) is the original Mystic Timber smoking wand, designed for use in the household chill room, especially when sharing your smoke with others. The first Blunt Beasts involved an eleven-inch wand and had a single set of grips near the smoking end. As the style evolved through time, and extensive field testing, a second set of grips were added near the base to facilitate passing, and the shaft was shortened to a more comfortable eight inches.

This size is useful in a variety of smoking situations and is Bruce’s personal favorite. Like all of our smoking wands, the Blunt Beast keeps the structural integrity of your handroll intact, makes it last longer, and keeps the smell off your fingers."
